data.description: Super 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath, 1600 sq ft+ cape with a full basement and garage on a huge lot across from the lake! Very large eat in kitchen that extends into the four season room that is currently being used as the dining area and family room which opens out to the level side yard. 2 bedrooms downstairs and two bedrooms upstairs, full baths on the main floor and basement. Across the street from Lake Musconetcong and very close to Port Morris and Arbolino Parks. Needs some TLC but is a very good solid home!
